              </p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </p>
        Prove that all points on or inside the circle whose equation is <m>\left( x - 1 \right)^2 + \left( y - 2 \right)^2 = 4</m> are inside the circle whose equation is <m>x^2 + y^2 = 26</m>.
      </li>
      <li xml:id="exer_insidecircle">
